{"tid":738132,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"jj插沙 求牙醫推介","createTime":"2018-07-11T09:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T08:48:26.000Z","uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b834236b8fd790e0e64f9aaadd87672fe0c358","tid":738132,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"蛀牙<br />\n好撚多隻<br />\n有隻蛀到得返一半<br />\n求牙醫推介<br />\n價錢唔好太貴就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇啲咩冇同新科技<br />\n又或者少痛<br />\n又或者有冇啲診所係可以環境好親切同埋俾你聽住歌做治療<br />\n即係啲醫生見到你情況好嚴重然後就話鳩你話做乜咁遲先來睇醫生<br />\n有冇d情況就算好差都只會係講問題不大然後就幫你整有m(心理輔導)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有冇啲係唔使打麻醉針<br />\n但係會落麻醉藥<br />\n因為真係一啲痛受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b3b9ce2582ff2e5f6e90e676fa2e7918aa1adc","tid":738132,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"應該普遍會落麻醉藥,補牙既話佢應該會有兩種材料比你選<br />\n一種比較似牙既原色但無咁襟用,而且貴D<br />\n一種用銀粉比較襟用,而且平D,但好似話對健康有少少唔好"},{"pid":"b74ef3e0ef091691dd82b8ddd9032b82093ae9f4","tid":738132,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b3b9ce2582ff2e5f6e90e676fa2e7918aa1adc","tid":738132,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"應該普遍會落麻醉藥,補牙既話佢應該會有兩種材料比你選<br />\n一種比較似牙既原色但無咁襟用,而且貴D<br />\n一種用銀粉比較襟用,而且平D,但好似話對健康有少少唔好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"怕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be77b34a3fac9b19633f9cb03b236db8119d8ab7","tid":738132,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74ef3e0ef091691dd82b8ddd9032b82093ae9f4","tid":738132,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote